{"tid":1439532,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸武警混入香港警隊 約2千人","createTime":"2019-08-10T06:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T06:53:00.000Z","uid":285112,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8796e41ba9855eddafe7fbf83b63fb19f98d0ab8","tid":1439532,"uid":285112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:48:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.singthepress.com/archives/263\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.singthepress.com%2Farchives%2F263&d=sJhP54gyZlpQHD%2BOhJ68s9g1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=00f4834e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.singthepress.com/archives/263</a><br />\n<br />\n 我有啲相信，如果唔係張建宗就唔使死狗咁道歉啦。黑嘅就派所謂嘅同鄉會落嚟香港打人，白嘅就派武警混入警察裏面暴力鎮壓示威者。 務求打到所有示威嘅人都怕左，唔敢再上街，唔敢再反對。<br />\n<br />\n有冇insider內幕？有冇辦法搞大佢？ 等全世界都知共產黨唔使出解放軍都有辦法嚟香港搞事。"},{"pid":"41b41d915b4236333059f1c2ca6f31e4be8ea4d9","tid":1439532,"uid":284581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T06:53:00.000Z","msg":"琴晚老友個警fd講咗速犬有一半係老解"}]}